description:
Balbir Singh of Morgan and Hayes Real Estate is delighted to present this “RARE AS A HENS TEETH - POTENTIAL DEVELOPMENT OPPORTUNITY” in Armadale’s much desired, and rapidly expanding, corridor.

This large approximately 11,000 square meter combined four (4) lot parcel of land offers multiple potential development opportunities to the astute investor / developer. Two lots front Albany Highway and the remaining two lots have street frontage onto Owtram Road.

The combined sale includes the following four properties:

- 3201 Albany Highway, Armadale
- 3203 Albany Highway, Armadale
- 59 Owtram Road, Armadale
- 61 Owtram Road, Armadale

The City of Armadale has advised the properties are all currently zoned R15/60.

For further details please contact Balbir today.

DISCLAIMER: Whilst every care has been taken with the preparation of the particulars contained in the information supplied, believed to be correct, neither the Agent nor the client nor servants of both, guarantee their accuracy. Interested persons are advised to make their own enquiries and satisfy themselves in all respects. The particulars contained are not intended to form part of any contract. Errors and omissions excluded.
